Resource Profile: ServiceRequest LE

Official URL: http://minsal.cl/listaespera/StructureDefinition/ServiceRequestLE Version: 0.1.3
Standards status: Draft Maturity Level: 0 Computable Name: ServiceRequestLE

ServiceRequest LE recurso utilizado para la representación de los datos de la interconsulta.

Usage:

  • Use this Resource Profile: Bundle Agendar LE, Bundle Atender LE, BundleInicio LE, Bundle Priorizar LE... Show 3 more, Bundle Referencia LE, Bundle Revisar LE and Bundle Terminar LE
  • Refer to this Resource Profile: Encounter Atender LE and MessageHeader LE
  • Examples for this Resource Profile: ServiceRequest/EjemploServiceRequest, ServiceRequest/EjemploServiceRequestAgendar, ServiceRequest/EjemploServiceRequestAtender, ServiceRequest/EjemploServiceRequestPriorizar... Show 3 more, ServiceRequest/EjemploServiceRequestReferenciada, ServiceRequest/EjemploServiceRequestRevisar and ServiceRequest/EjemploServiceRequestTerminar
